Premium Free TV has launched its VIDAA app, which allows Hisense TV owners to watch their favourite shows at no charge. Premium Free TV is a service that offers 20 channels – including a variety of movies, series, telenovelas, sports, and other content that spans genres such as kids, comedy, lifestyle, reality, documentaries, faith, and education. “We have partnered with specialist tech companies to ensure our channel offerings are widely available for streaming, allowing viewers to watch anywhere at any time,” said Premium Free CEO Craig Kelly. “Our partnership with VIDAA allows the app to be live on their platform on selected Hisense TV screens.” The service is also available on smartphone and on the web, and prides itself on having extensive programming made in Africa, by Africans, and aimed at the African viewer. This lets it showcase the cream of the continent’s talent. This is then complemented by the best international content from Hollywood and beyond, and makes Premium Free TV a must-see if you own a Hisense TV. Premium Free TV viewers love what’s on offer from the service, and had the following to say about it: If you’d like to join the Premium Free TV family and enjoy the extensive range of programming on offer, all you need to do is download the app on your phone, or launch the pre-installed app on selected VIDAA-enabled smart TVs from Hisense. Watch Premium Free TV today – Click here to learn more.